title: Golden Eagle softball prepares for 2022 campaign - Tennessee Tech - Tennessee Tech
content: Golden Eagle softball prepares for 2022 campaign - Tennessee Tech  Tennessee Tech
description:
COOKEVILLE, Tenn. – There will be a lot of new faces and familiar foes on the diamond this season as the Tennessee Tech softball team prepares to open its 2022 campaign.

The 37th season of Golden Eagle softball will feature four pre-conference tournaments – including the first one in Cookeville since the 2002 campaign – as well as a couple of power conference opponents including in-state foe Tennessee before starting another exciting season of Ohio Valley Conference competition.

All times listed are Central.
